data.name: lblAir.ToolTip
data.value: Air Signs are rational, social, and love communication and relationships with other people. They are thinkers, friendly, intellectual, communicatvie, and analytial. The love philosophical discussions, social gatherings and good books. They enjoy giving advice, but they can also be very superficial.

data.name: lblHealth.Text
data.value: The transit of the day increases your affection for a partner, for children, even pets - anything that you shower with love will feel the effect of this planetary energy. However, don't expect it to be received with a big thank you! Sometimes people take what you give in a way that makes you wonder whether they know how precious your feelings are. Don't let that make you feel resentful - just mention this concern and all will be well. Be sure to drink lots of water to help keep your emotional state flexible.

data.name: lblLuck.Text
data.value: Work that engages your mind and helps you think as well as stimulating other people’s minds is the best line of work for you to engage in. You also like variety and do something that is going to uplift people generally. You have a wealth of ideas and can progressively put forward concepts that can not only improve the quality of the work but also the way in which people work together. All of these wonderful attributes will contribute to your luck in life.

data.name: lblTravel.Text
data.value: Your famed friendliness is in full force on Monday and Tuesday, allowing you to experience the culture of where you are in an extraordinary way. These are the kinds of connections you'll treasure, so take lots of pictures and give out your email address with abandon. By midweek, you'll need to slow down; even you require a little privacy now and then. Group activities are favored this weekend -- and taking an architectural or environmental tour can lead you to fascinating people who share your values.

data.name: lblMoney.Text
data.value: It's a time of much change for you. Your workplace may be moving in a more enjoyable direction of late, and you're able to create some peace for yourself in the midst of others' stress. But the Universe demands nothing less than complete transformation when it comes to your spending patterns with family members, kids, or romantic partners. A little gets your point across. You don't have to go overboard.

data.name: lblCareer.Text
data.value: This week marks an important yearly beginning for you. The cosmos is asking you to wipe the slate clean and start fresh. You are in control of your destiny. Take a new route. Success is yours if you aren't afraid to take a risk.

data.name: lblLove.Text
data.value: Now's a good time to loosen up and drop some of your petty concerns about your sweetheart. If you have been feeling uptight, or have been blaming your partner (current or prospective) for all kinds of things that perhaps they are not entirely guilty of, then it may be time to give them a break. Rather than complaining, try taking them out for a well-deserved meal.
